{{unreferenced|date=May 2017}} {{Infobox scientist | name = Stephan von Breuning | image = Breuning SN.jpg | image_size = | alt = | caption = | birth_date = 21 November 1894 | birth_place = [[Vienna]], [[Austria-Hungary]] | death_date = {{Death date and age|1983|3|11|1894|11|21|df=yes}} | death_place = [[Paris]], [[France]] | resting_place = | resting_place_coordinates = <!-- {{Coord|LAT|LONG|type:landmark|display=inline,title}} --> | residence = France | citizenship = | nationality = | fields = [[Entomology]] | workplaces = | alma_mater = | thesis_title = | thesis_url = | thesis_year = | doctoral_advisor = | academic_advisors = | doctoral_students = | notable_students = | known_for = Études sur les Lamiaires | author_abbrev_bot = | author_abbrev_zoo = | influences = | influenced = | awards = | signature = | signature_alt = | website = | footnotes = | spouse = }}
'''Stephan von Breuning''' (21 November 1894 &ndash; 11 March 1983) was an Austrian [[entomologist]] who specialised in [[Coleoptera]], particularly [[Cerambycidae]].
==Career== An amateur working on the rich collections of the [[Muséum national d'Histoire naturelle]], he described 7894 [[taxon|taxa]] of Cerambycidae.
==Works== The complete list of his entomological works has been published in the ''[[Bulletin de la Société Sciences Nat]]'', number 41.[https://web.archive.org/web/20110624044100/http://www.insects.demon.co.uk/bullsn/bull-1.html]
One of his most famous remains ''Études sur les Lamiaires'', published in [[Novitates entomologicae]], 1934-1946.
==Personal life== He gave the photo shown together with a text to be published after his death. Von Breuning lived with his wife in a small studio rue Durantin, Paris 18ème at the top of an old building.
==Further reading== {{refbegin}} * {{cite journal|last1=Kuschel|first1=Gillermo|last2=Emberson|first2=Rowan M.|title=Notes on ''Hybolasius trigonellaris'' Hutton from the Chatham Islands (Coleoptera: Cerambycidae: Lamiinae)|journal=New Zealand Entomologist|date=2008|volume=31|issue=1|pages=89–92|doi=10.1080/00779962.2008.9722170}} * {{cite journal|last1=Meunier|first1=Jean-Yves|last2=Téocchi|first2=Pierre|title=Addenda et corrigenda à la liste des publications de Stephan von Breuning (1894 – 1983) avec une notice biographique|journal=L'Entomologiste|date=2015|volume=71|issue=5|pages=317–320|url=https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Jean_Yves_Meunier/publication/289529570_Addenda_et_corrigenda_a_la_liste_des_publications_de_Stephan_von_Breuning_1894-1983_avec_une_notice_biographique/links/568ef01508aef987e567e745.pdf}} * {{cite journal|last1=Blumenthal|first1=C. L.|last2=Heinz|first2=W.|title=Zum Gedenken an Stephan von Breuning|journal=Entomologische Zeitschrift mit Insektenbörse|date=1984|volume=94|page=32}} * {{cite journal|last1=von Breuning|first1=Stephan|title=Stephan von Breuning 1894–1983, Notice autobiographique et liste des publications|journal=Bulletin de la Société Sciences Nat|date=1984|volume=41|pages=1–17}} {{refend}}
